30:26.868 --> 30:29.496
Mylo? Claggor?

30:30.413 --> 30:31.748
Powder?

30:38.463 --> 30:41.132
Nobody wins in war, Vi.

30:48.473 --> 30:49.474
What are we gonna do?

30:50.976 --> 30:52.435
The Enforcers will come back.

30:54.145 --> 30:59.484
I... I don't know.
I'll, uh, I'll figure it out.

31:50.827 --> 31:51.995
